    <p>Add <a href="/addnews">news</a>.</p>
    <p>Update <a href="/updatenews">news</a>.</p>
    <p>Delete all <a href="/news/delete/all">news</a>.</p>
    <p>Delete news by id - use /news/delete/{id} endpoint.</p>

    <a href="/logout">Log out</a>
